oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Continued performance by the Bluegrass Dropouts from other side of tape / Vassar Clements on fiddle and Fred Weis on fiddle and comments, 1968-07-?? In Nashville TN / Kentucky Colonels at Ash Grove, Los Angeles, California on April 11, 1967. Personnel listed Roland White (mandolin); Clarence White (guitar); Eric White (bass); Bob Warford (banjo); Dennis Morris (guitar). Audio restricted. Contact for access.
